The paper deals with pattern matching and image processing, which are common topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and multimedia (cs.MM). The use of a non-linear model and consistent operations with the human visual system suggest that the paper may also belong to the information theory (cs.IT) and graphics (cs.GR) sub-categories. Finally, the paper's focus on defining a metric and its use for pattern matching may also make it relevant to the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category.
